SE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DQ\" title=\"Daqo New Energy Corp.\">DQ</a></span>) is a Chinese company among the leading global producers of polysilicon, a material used for solar panel manufacturing. The sharp polysilicon price decline between 2023 and 2024 negatively impacted both revenue and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168519491/image_2168519491.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742766-daqo-new-energy-deeply-undervalued-amid-short-term-challenges", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 10:51:30"}, {"id": "4742765", "title": "Stagwell: Acquisitions, EPS Growth, Proven Business Model, And Undervalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/1650675754/photo/set-of-bundles-of-money-and-gold-coins-floating-on-pastel-violet-background.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=YZsVwEoz_Xn8tcu0BSX3Rk3TIcVuSuq2Es8yW_fADko=\" alt=\"Set of Bundles of money and gold coins floating on pastel violet background\" data-id=\"1650675754\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Sedykh/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Stagwell Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STGW\" title=\"Stagwell Inc.\">STGW</a></span>) reported a number of new acquisitions in 2023 and 2024, which may bring net sales growth in 2025 and 2026. With the internationalization efforts, network of affiliates, diversified customer base of 4k employees, and previous</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742765-stagwell-acquisitions-eps-growth-proven-business-model-and-undervalued", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 10:45:59"}, {"id": "4742777", "title": "Stock Market 'Fear Gauge' Plunges; Investors Expect Rally To Persist Into 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Arrow points on Fear at Fear and Greed Index, white background, copy space\" data-id=\"1388507528\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"768px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">photoman</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>A key measure of fear in the stock market has fallen to its lowest levels in months even as questions about the incoming Trump administration swirl, geopolitical uncertainty stays elevated, and the economic path forward appears to filled with hurdles.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388507528/image_1388507528.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742777-stock-market-fear-gauge-plunges-investors-expect-rally-persist-into-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 10:40:00"}, {"id": "4742770", "title": "International Equities: Opportunities Beyond U.S. Dominance", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A world globe marked with several national flag pins\" data-id=\"1303046106\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5220px\" height=\"3480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By George Maris, CFA, Chief Investment Officer, Global Equities and Scott Leiberton, CFA, Managing Director, Client Portfolio Manager</em></p> <p>On the back of strong economic growth and a steady wave of technology advancements, U.S. equities have outperformed global equities for</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742770-international-equities-opportunities-beyond-us-dominance", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 10:20:00"}]}